href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/novo-next-generation-shot-helps-patients-lose-23-of-weight\" rel=\"nofollow\">news came out</a> that its obesity drug \u2014 CagriSema \u2014 delivered disappointing trial results, as Bloomberg reported an hour</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745572-novo-nordisk-a-rare-buying-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:15:17", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745566", "title": "7 Upcoming Dividend Increases", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Growth graph made of taller and taller gifts with last pillar being a Christmas tree\" data-id=\"2177999675\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"878px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024p