20w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Vera Tikhonova</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Ford\u2019s (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/F\" title=\"Ford Motor Company\">F</a></span>) 6.2% dividend yield has been the focus of income investors looking for good yield in a market that has become quite expensive according to several metrics. Ford\u2019s dividend yield is significantly higher than the mere 1.2% yield</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745563-ford-dont-fall-for-this-dividend-play", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:02:20", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4744637", "title": "How I Would Retire Early With $1 Million Today", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"1 Million Celebration Balloons with Confetti\" data-id=\"1401505902\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=ge