g Yellow Group", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Golden egg in egg cup\" data-id=\"130409767\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1151px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andy Roberts/OJO Images via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>One of my favorite investment themes for the coming decade is self storage in Europe.</p> <p>The reason why I like it so much is that the European self storage market is today about</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745449-my-highest-conviction-reit-investment-idea-big-yellow-group", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 16:35:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745529", "title": "Soho House: Could Go Private Again Only 3 Years After IPO", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"View of Soho House Club with lens flares in Pera area\" data-id=\"646653958\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1083px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">theendup</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Soho House &amp; Co (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SHCO\" title=\"Soho House &amp; Co Inc.\">SHCO</a></span>) recently announced its quarterly results which also included the company's confirmation of a buyout offer and this resulted in the company's share price to appreciate close to 50% in one day. While this wasn't</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745529-soho-house-could-go-private-again-only-3-years-after-ipo", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 16:30:45", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745551", "title": "How To Use Leverage To Boost Your Returns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rear view of young man walking towards detour\" data-id=\"1253985593\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8660px\" height=\"5773px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Leverage can be a powerful tool in increasing your returns, but it must be used very carefully. This brief guide will attempt to cover margin, hedging, and related issues.</p> <h2>Financing Your Investments</h2> <p>In theory, if your expected returns</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745551-how-to-use-leverage-to-boost-your-returns", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 16:24:25", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745550", "title": "TransUnion: A Perfect Stocking Stuffer For Your Portfolio This Christmas", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up of stack of credit cards\" data-id=\"88621207\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1153px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jp